      <Conflict>The guards are terrified by the ghost's appearance</Conflict>
      <Outcome>They decide to tell Prince Hamlet about the ghost</Outcome>
      <SceneContent>[i]The battlements of Elsinore Castle. A cold night.[/i]

BERNARDO: Who's there?

FRANCISCO: Nay, answer me. Stand and unfold yourself.

The ghost appears, wearing armor like the dead King. The guards stand frozen in fear.</SceneContent>
